      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition car that looks presentable from a distance but shows clear age and use up close. The paint, body, and interior all have noticeable wear, and it should be expected to have cosmetic flaws and typical older-car needs. That said, it appears complete and usable as a driver, making it a reasonable choice for someone who wants an affordable example to enjoy as-is while improving over time.",
