    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept, honest driver in good overall condition. It presents nicely inside and out, with the kind of normal cosmetic wear and minor age-related imperfections you\u2019d expect on a used car, but nothing that suggests it has been neglected. The interior appears clean and usable, the exterior shows well overall, and it should make a solid, straightforward car for its next owner. Not a show car or fully refreshed example, just a good, properly presentable vehicle that looks to have been cared for and is ready to be enjoyed as-is.",
