    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and straightforward, this vehicle offers an affordable path into ownership for the value-focused buyer. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical option for basic commuting, errands, or as a starter vehicle. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive transportation with honest character and strong value at this price point, this is a smart buy.",
