      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car being sold as-is, and priced to make sense. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it could be a great budget runabout, project, or parts car for the right person. If you\u2019re handy with cars or just need something affordable to tinker with, this one has potential and is offered by someone who\u2019d rather be upfront than oversell it. Simple, straightforward, and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with a strong, eager-running powertrain and a chassis that still feels planted on the road. Starts, runs, and moves out well, with the kind of mechanical honesty enthusiasts appreciate. Shows wear consistent with age and use, but it has good bones, useful parts value, and plenty of upside for someone who wants an affordable entry point. Ideal for a hands-on buyer looking for a capable fixer, weekend project, or inexpensive transportation with character.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
